{"tid":1674024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[WE CONNECT] 支持林鄭月娥專區","createTime":"2019-10-25T03:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T03:35:10.000Z","uid":26332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c28370b5316645c2c7498983e3b67be4bb5943f","tid":1674024,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:30:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>華春瑩撐林鄭言論「被消失」 四中全會前夕不尋常</strong><br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》（FT）周三報道，北京計劃於明年3月更換香港特首林鄭月娥，中國外交部發言人華春瑩其後在例行新聞發布會上指有關報道是「別有用心的政治謠言」，以一貫口吻強調中央政府堅定支持林鄭，內地網站亦廣泛轉載。不過，中國外交部的官方文字紀錄未幾已經不見了華春瑩這段相關說法。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/politics/article/2284009/%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%A5%E7%91%A9%E6%92%90%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%8D+%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8B%E5%B8%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F2284009%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2598%25A5%25E7%2591%25A9%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E3%2580%258D%2B%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%25B8%25B8&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=3a8b2445\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/politics/article/2284009/%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%A5%E7%91%A9%E6%92%90%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%8D+%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8B%E5%B8%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港市民<ins>反對</ins>換特首！<br />\n<br />\n全力支持林鄭月娥為首的政府繼續執政！<br />\n<br />\n全力支持林鄭月娥帶領香港步向攬炒，全球抗共，WE CONNECT！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8a9f6ab43d239f10fb0a319f94f3dba74ef0dcb","tid":1674024,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T